flowchart TD
    A[Row mutated in Postgres<br/>INSERT / UPDATE / DELETE] --> B[WAL entry written]
    B --> C[Debezium reads logical<br/>replication slot pgoutput]
    C --> D{op code}
    D -- c/r create/read --> E[after image]
    D -- u update --> F[before + after image]
    D -- d delete --> G[before image + tombstone]
    E --> H[Avro-encode via Schema Registry]
    F --> H
    G --> H
    H --> I[(Kafka topic<br/>commerce.public.table)]
    I --> J[Spark Bronze append<br/>immutable log]
    J --> K[Spark Silver:<br/>dedup by PK, order by LSN]
    K --> L{is delete?}
    L -- yes --> M[MERGE ... WHEN MATCHED THEN DELETE]
    L -- no --> N[MERGE upsert if LSN newer]
    M --> O[(silver.table<br/>current state)]
    N --> O
    O --> P[Gold marts via dbt]
